{"id":290124,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-江苏南通如皋储祥山房屋今被强拆（图）/","date":"2013-04-22T07:30:49Z","modified":"2013-04-22T07:30:49Z","title":"维权网 | 江苏南通如皋储祥山房屋今被强拆（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）今天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>星期一）上午</span>9</span><span>点许，如皋储祥山</span><span>位于如皋市如城镇新王庄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>组</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">95</span><span>号的房屋</span><span>被当地政府强拆。在强拆过程中，储祥山和家属被关进拆迁指挥部。储祥山的妻子被打，现在还在医院里。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>储祥山的女儿得知消息后，一连打了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多个电话，向</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警，但民警拒绝出警。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，江苏省如皋经济开发区城市管理办公室工作人员在储祥山的房屋前贴出《限期拆除通知书》，称其为违法建筑，限令二天内自行拆除该房屋。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>储祥山在自己宅基地上盖的房屋已经有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多年了，一夜之间竟成了违法建筑。储祥山老人向如皋市政府提起了行政复议申请，并申请停止执行。复议期间，在事先没有通知的情况下，储祥山的房屋被强拆了。在此之前，储家经常受到骚扰，拆迁指挥部派人前来逼储祥山拆房腾地。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ONJvmp8AYms/UXTT7u5v5eI/AAAAAAAAgr4/qFHrdm6zc88/s1600/DSCN2534.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ONJvmp8AYms/UXTT7u5v5eI/AAAAAAAAgr4/qFHrdm6zc88/s400/DSCN2534.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-40S03nrCdAk/UXTT9ArLICI/AAAAAAAAgsA/3QyoxUFNncw/s1600/DSCN2542.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-40S03nrCdAk/UXTT9ArLICI/AAAAAAAAgsA/3QyoxUFNncw/s400/DSCN2542.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div><